| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0483 — Recovery Inhibition (medusalocker)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 1ed75a37-c5a3-5ac5-a128-3aa697309f4b"
